divs: Sighting DetailsI was bike riding with my boyfriend in O'Neil Regional Park in Trabuco Canyon, CA and we stopped for some sightseeing. Took a few pictures of the landscape and later that evening downloaded them to our laptop. That's when we noticed a "spot" in one of the pictures. We hadn't noticed it at the time of taking the shot. To us it doesn't really look like a bird or a plane so we hope you could help us find out what it was! Attached you'll find the picture.
Summary: UFO appears in a picture we took on a bike ride
trends: There have been no other sightings in Trabuco Canyon
This sighting has never been favorited.
